                    on. He was also very patient with us as the design would
                    change at various times throughout the process. Within a day
                    of them finishing the deck we have had random neighbors on
                    our block stop and say how great the deck looks. We will
                    definitely be calling him again the next couple years as
                    more and more updates are needed on our house. Great job
                    guys!
                  </p>
